{"tid":2225550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高等法院原訟法庭法官【包華禮 Bharwaney 】獲林鄭頒發「銀紫荊星章」","createTime":"2020-10-01T11:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T10:14:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7321dd31fde78eab86147933d616e9f0e9d4f8d0","tid":2225550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/531879/org/aaf31404eff72ef2dca44f342486f854.png/XFxT9geWexHE6dEPHm2zVcR2uwx2r76YjORFzIzkRcw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F531879%2Forg%2Faaf31404eff72ef2dca44f342486f854.png%2FXFxT9geWexHE6dEPHm2zVcR2uwx2r76YjORFzIzkRcw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=7c9d96b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獲頒銀紫荊星章有２２人，包括高等法院原訟法庭法官包華禮、廠商會會長吳宏斌、前醫管局行政總裁梁栢賢、前大律師公會主席譚允芝，以及多位金融及商界名人，如信德集團行政主席何超瓊、證監會行政總裁歐達禮、港交所行政總裁李小加等。<br />\n<br />\n今年金紫荊星章的得主共有１５人，包括多位金融及政界名人，如滙豐亞太區行政總裁王冬勝、前警務處處長盧偉聰、工聯會榮譽會長陳婉嫻、全國政協常委譚錦球等。"},{"pid":"89afdd295541b089490e33740d72ac01bb13048c","tid":2225550,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"香港城巿大學四年級男生，聲稱三年前佔旺清場後的「鳩嗚」運動期間，他與女友回家時在旺角被捕，更稱遭男警粗暴抓下體非禮，早前指警方嚴重侵犯人權，入稟向警務處處長索償1200萬元，案件今日在高院提訊，法官<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">包華禮</span></span></strong>指通常受傷至癱瘓才會獲千萬賠償，質疑男生只是手部有抓痕，索償千萬不合理，更直言若要示威，應走上街，非到法庭，即將案押後7月21日，並要求原告與其父母下次也須到庭，質疑其父母是否有足夠財力助兒子興訴。"},{"pid":"f24d75fe01f10801eabcf5d05384a45804fa8285","tid":2225550,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:21:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73fa102c117ca67001e9eea7c3c813e41c1cf15b","tid":2225550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d06adc6553897f2d8230cc6b955be215e8ada7","tid":2225550,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"有打手係另一post spin到夠年資就有授勳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2225557/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2225557/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%8A%80%E7%B4%AB%E8%8D%8A%E6%98%9F%E7%AB%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%258A%2580%25E7%25B4%25AB%25E8%258D%258A%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25AB%25A0&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=b95a2a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%8A%80%E7%B4%AB%E8%8D%8A%E6%98%9F%E7%AB%A0</a><br />\n司法系統同代人大把人無份<br />\n-------<br />\n破紀錄687人獲勳章 政治分贓警暴警謊94人上榜<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">唔通消防救護無人退休?<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e320928a6d95582eff23d194aa0bd1c3d62240f6","tid":2225550,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"真正重點係抹黑受害人<br />\n'更直言若要示威，應走上街，非到法庭'<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>姐係暗示異見者告警察就係宣示政治立場的誣告<br />\n令到班狗覺得有高院法官照而去強姦女仔</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e1a76706e2881e3c8aacb9aa63f97caf2a41cf74","tid":2225550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}